WEBVTT

01:37.870 --> 01:41.020
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.060 --> 01:43.979
[Episode 35]

01:46.509 --> 01:49.759
This is our first cooperation.

01:50.560 --> 01:52.620
But I don't want it to be the last time.

01:52.759 --> 01:54.310
I hope we can create more

01:54.310 --> 01:55.120
next time.

01:55.509 --> 01:56.970
More surprises together.

01:57.229 --> 01:58.120
Can we?

02:01.580 --> 02:02.250
Yes.

02:02.710 --> 02:03.600
Thank you.

02:35.920 --> 02:38.290
Come on, cheers.

03:06.060 --> 03:08.070
You guys talk. I'll go over there.

03:09.970 --> 03:11.500
Congratulations, Kevin.

03:16.220 --> 03:17.150
I'm sorry

03:17.150 --> 03:20.079
for making you ride
the roller coaster with me again.

03:20.140 --> 03:21.800
If the boss himself,

03:21.800 --> 03:23.560
who almost flew off
the roller coaster, doesn't mind,

03:23.560 --> 03:24.870
why should I mind?

03:25.890 --> 03:28.160
Although I was singing
a different tune the whole time,

03:28.160 --> 03:29.440
it turns out

03:29.460 --> 03:31.060
this adventure was worth it.

03:31.710 --> 03:32.760
I meant no harm.

03:33.630 --> 03:35.010
Maybe I'm just old.

03:35.970 --> 03:38.350
Why are you suddenly getting sentimental?

03:38.350 --> 03:39.829
No matter what, Cindy,

03:39.850 --> 03:41.300
you'll always be my CFO.

03:41.329 --> 03:42.810
That will never change.

03:42.990 --> 03:43.829
You know what?

03:44.630 --> 03:45.840
I used to think

03:45.870 --> 03:48.400
that was the most beautiful
love confession.

03:48.980 --> 03:49.579
Really.

03:50.130 --> 03:52.370
I actually gave up marrying you

03:52.400 --> 03:54.329
to be your CFO in your company

03:54.360 --> 03:55.470
to secure a longer

03:55.490 --> 03:57.900
and more stable relationship.

03:58.760 --> 03:59.880
Tell me,

04:00.270 --> 04:02.220
do you think I'm ridiculous

04:02.240 --> 04:03.300
and unreasonable?

04:03.600 --> 04:05.310
If you suddenly confess your love,

04:05.310 --> 04:07.240
I wouldn't know what to do.

04:08.440 --> 04:10.160
What are you so proud of?

04:10.900 --> 04:14.430
I'm just sighing
about my past childishness.

04:14.690 --> 04:16.920
I have many suitors now too.

04:16.940 --> 04:18.450
I know. I know.

04:21.410 --> 04:22.710
It's just that when I saw

04:22.710 --> 04:24.670
the way you looked at Xu Miyu,

04:24.910 --> 04:27.320
I had a bystander's perspective

04:27.340 --> 04:29.400
and clearly saw what love looks like.

04:29.400 --> 04:30.460
So tomorrow,

04:30.950 --> 04:33.010
are you really not going back with us?

04:33.830 --> 04:34.920
I want to stay here for a while

04:34.920 --> 04:35.800
to keep my father company.

04:35.800 --> 04:36.560
You think I don't know

04:36.560 --> 04:38.240
you stayed for Ms. Xu?

04:41.120 --> 04:43.310
I wish you happiness soon.

04:43.720 --> 04:44.520
You too.

04:50.130 --> 04:50.860
I'm leaving.

05:03.930 --> 05:04.940
Thanks to you this time.

05:04.940 --> 05:05.650
Miyu.

05:05.670 --> 05:06.940
We'll be leaving then.

05:10.020 --> 05:11.260
Let's dance.

05:13.040 --> 05:14.160
It's fine, come on.

05:55.430 --> 05:56.920
Did you and Ji Feng

05:56.940 --> 05:57.750
have a falling out

05:57.750 --> 05:59.480
because of the art exhibition?

06:02.390 --> 06:03.850
Is it that obvious?

06:05.140 --> 06:06.390
Your expression just now

06:06.390 --> 06:07.870
was like David Jagger's

06:07.870 --> 06:09.430
melancholy Catherine.

06:15.140 --> 06:15.920
You said earlier

06:15.920 --> 06:18.380
you didn't dare to
start a certain painting.

06:18.870 --> 06:21.000
You were talking about Ji Feng, right?

06:24.240 --> 06:26.890
But it felt wrong to start.

06:28.740 --> 06:29.720
If it were me,

06:29.720 --> 06:32.150
I would protect you immediately,

06:33.070 --> 06:35.070
no matter what kind of enemy we face.

06:37.200 --> 06:38.330
I mean it.

06:39.050 --> 06:41.159
I've also experienced
failed relationships.

06:41.159 --> 06:43.040
My biggest realization now is that

06:43.040 --> 06:44.370
a good relationship

06:44.400 --> 06:46.680
isn't about how useful
the other person is,

06:46.680 --> 06:49.340
but about unconditional
trust and protection.

06:51.090 --> 06:52.090
What do you think?

07:15.720 --> 07:22.660
[East Changzhi Road] [Changzhi Road]

07:48.550 --> 07:50.300
♪ A flicker of dim light ♪

07:52.060 --> 07:53.710
♪ A bowl of warm soup ♪

07:55.890 --> 08:02.680
[East Changzhi Road] [Changzhi Road]

07:55.909 --> 07:57.690
♪ People in the city ♪

07:58.650 --> 08:01.590
♪ Squeezing into the hustle and bustle ♪

08:03.520 --> 08:05.330
♪ The palms of time ♪

08:07.250 --> 08:10.290
♪ Grinding away the simple days ♪

08:10.990 --> 08:13.510
♪ Sprinkling them into this busy world ♪

08:14.920 --> 08:16.980
♪ To be tasted, bit by bit ♪

08:18.480 --> 08:21.710
♪ Embracing this radiant world ♪

08:22.200 --> 08:25.230
♪ Keeps the heart from fading to grey ♪

08:24.450 --> 08:25.480
Are you okay?

08:25.500 --> 08:26.260
I'm fine.

08:25.830 --> 08:28.950
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

08:29.690 --> 08:32.309
♪ Intertwined within the mundane ♪

08:31.280 --> 08:32.090
Come in.

08:33.730 --> 08:36.919
♪ Let us bravely gather up ♪

08:37.590 --> 08:41.039
♪ The forgotten past ♪

08:41.950 --> 08:44.220
♪ There may be regrets ♪

08:45.880 --> 08:48.060
♪ There may be loneliness ♪

08:53.320 --> 08:54.310
Xu Miyu,

08:55.190 --> 08:56.380
thank you

08:57.530 --> 08:58.530
for staying.

09:04.800 --> 09:05.780
Sorry.

09:06.390 --> 09:07.240
Sorry.

09:08.390 --> 09:09.150
I'm fine.

09:09.520 --> 09:10.190
I'm fine.

09:10.870 --> 09:11.800
I can do it.

09:15.600 --> 09:16.800
Good evening, Mr. Ji.

09:17.050 --> 09:19.360
Do you need me to unlock the door for you?

09:18.340 --> 09:21.330
♪ Facing the unknown, lost in doubt ♪

09:22.070 --> 09:24.710
♪ A gentle warmth takes shape ♪

09:26.790 --> 09:28.710
♪ After all you've been through ♪

09:27.420 --> 09:27.990
No need.

09:29.990 --> 09:32.190
♪ Silver at your temples ♪

09:32.650 --> 09:33.510
That's enough.

09:33.580 --> 09:36.310
♪ Rows of uneven buildings ♪

09:35.130 --> 09:36.020
Thank you.

09:37.460 --> 09:39.740
♪ Have forgotten hope ♪

09:40.870 --> 09:46.090
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

09:41.850 --> 09:43.790
♪ We are in the glow of fireworks ♪

09:45.310 --> 09:47.210
♪ Lights bursting into bloom ♪

09:48.350 --> 09:51.740
♪ Embracing this radiant world ♪

09:52.050 --> 09:55.130
♪ Keeps the heart from fading to grey ♪

09:54.610 --> 09:56.950
I know I missed the best opportunity.

09:55.680 --> 09:58.990
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

09:57.180 --> 09:58.760
I don't want to miss it again.

09:58.760 --> 10:00.440
Because I like you.

09:59.540 --> 10:02.310
♪ Intertwined within the mundane ♪

10:03.600 --> 10:06.490
♪ Let us bravely gather up ♪

10:07.170 --> 10:10.400
♪ The forgotten past ♪

10:13.660 --> 10:16.030
♪ Walking through this world ♪

10:17.730 --> 10:21.730
♪ Leaving no regrets behind ♪

10:19.910 --> 10:21.350
Thank you for your hard work, everyone.

10:21.350 --> 10:23.210
The art exhibition was a complete success.

10:23.210 --> 10:25.760
It's a great start for Q3.

10:26.400 --> 10:27.080
However,

10:27.260 --> 10:29.880
regarding the safety incident
that occurred during the exhibition,

10:29.880 --> 10:31.390
we will absolutely not compromise.

10:31.390 --> 10:33.030
It must be dealt with seriously.

10:33.030 --> 10:35.690
Now I will announce
the disciplinary decision.

10:41.080 --> 10:42.800
Qian Xun, former director
of the sales department,

10:42.800 --> 10:43.980
during the art exhibition,

10:43.980 --> 10:46.400
was found to have committed
serious disciplinary violations.

10:44.740 --> 10:47.510
[Purong Hotel]

10:46.530 --> 10:47.320
The circumstances are serious

10:47.320 --> 10:49.180
and have caused adverse effects.

10:49.550 --> 10:51.080
In accordance with the Purong Hotel

10:51.080 --> 10:53.080
employee management regulations,

10:53.600 --> 10:55.240
he has been dismissed.

11:19.120 --> 11:21.510
Huang Chengmin, former director
of the finance department,

11:21.510 --> 11:23.390
is suspected of conspiring

11:23.390 --> 11:24.850
in Qian Xun's misconduct.

11:25.510 --> 11:28.240
The hotel's executive office
has unanimously decided

11:28.240 --> 11:31.240
to terminate Huang Chengmin's
employment contract.

11:35.120 --> 11:37.000
The above penalties take effect

11:37.360 --> 11:38.510
from the date of this announcement.

11:38.510 --> 11:41.110
I hope other departments
take this as a warning

11:41.120 --> 11:42.980
and don't cause any more trouble.

11:44.000 --> 11:44.790
Liu Zidong.

11:45.630 --> 11:47.600
You will act as the Finance Director

11:47.600 --> 11:49.270
and take over Huang Chengmin's work.

11:49.270 --> 11:49.870
Yes.

11:51.720 --> 11:53.960
As for the new Sales Director,

12:01.240 --> 12:02.270
I will make the decision

12:02.270 --> 12:04.840
after discussing it
with the HR Department.

12:27.400 --> 12:28.150
Mr. Wei.

12:43.150 --> 12:43.870
Aunt.

12:44.240 --> 12:45.390
How long are you going to let Ji Feng

12:45.390 --> 12:47.270
continue to make waves?

12:47.790 --> 12:49.510
Feng Kaixin, Qian Xun,

12:49.510 --> 12:50.640
and Huang Chengmin.

12:50.790 --> 12:51.720
Before he came,

12:51.720 --> 12:53.120
they were all the pillars

12:53.290 --> 12:54.870
and heroes of the hotel.

12:55.360 --> 12:55.960
And now?

12:56.790 --> 12:58.120
He drove them all away.

12:59.390 --> 13:00.600
His actions

13:00.960 --> 13:02.590
are clearly targeting me.

13:02.610 --> 13:03.120
No,

13:03.600 --> 13:05.000
he is also targeting you.

13:07.910 --> 13:09.270
I know exactly

13:09.830 --> 13:12.140
who's targeting me and who's trying to

13:13.390 --> 13:15.480
hollow out Purong Hotel.

13:17.430 --> 13:18.550
Aunt,

13:18.790 --> 13:20.960
don't be fooled by him.

13:21.510 --> 13:22.980
I'm the one who hired him.

13:23.750 --> 13:25.080
But you,

13:25.430 --> 13:27.750
I understand you less and less.

13:31.670 --> 13:32.110
Fine.

13:32.110 --> 13:33.750
I admit I'm stupid

13:33.750 --> 13:35.350
and have no business talent.

13:35.470 --> 13:36.150
But what about Ji Feng?

13:36.150 --> 13:37.550
What's so good about him?

13:37.930 --> 13:39.140
He's dictatorial,

13:39.170 --> 13:39.910
arrogant,

13:39.910 --> 13:41.240
and dislikes everyone.

13:41.270 --> 13:43.120
He fired 2 of my best men at once.

13:43.120 --> 13:43.790
Aunt.

13:44.350 --> 13:45.000
If he wants to frame someone,

13:45.000 --> 13:46.290
he can always find an excuse.

13:46.290 --> 13:48.870
The charges he made up
are completely baseless.

13:48.870 --> 13:50.080
I think

13:50.100 --> 13:52.230
an outsider of unknown origin like him

13:52.600 --> 13:54.440
is the real threat to the hotel.

13:55.550 --> 13:56.510
Siyuan.

13:57.270 --> 13:58.600
Why is your thinking

13:58.660 --> 14:00.470
more old-fashioned than mine?

14:01.250 --> 14:02.830
Our Purong Hotel

14:02.960 --> 14:06.240
has never been
a complacent small workshop.

14:06.880 --> 14:07.880
Embracing the new

14:07.900 --> 14:09.330
is the important quality
of our Purong Hotel

14:09.330 --> 14:12.520
that allows us to gain
a foothold in Shanghai.

14:13.120 --> 14:14.870
You're so territorial

14:15.350 --> 14:16.870
and old-fashioned.

14:17.080 --> 14:18.740
If I leave Purong Hotel to you,

14:19.390 --> 14:20.670
will it be okay?

14:32.180 --> 14:33.020
Aunt.

14:34.080 --> 14:35.130
I understand now.

14:36.520 --> 14:37.920
From the very beginning,

14:38.550 --> 14:40.010
you had it all figured out.

14:40.580 --> 14:42.780
You just wanted to kick me aside, right?

14:44.270 --> 14:45.360
Siyuan,

14:45.800 --> 14:47.850
everything has a cause and effect.

14:48.440 --> 14:51.360
I personally handed
the Purong Hotel over to you.

14:51.760 --> 14:53.490
But you disappointed me.

14:54.010 --> 14:55.810
Then why did you only tell me now?

14:56.600 --> 14:57.840
Why did you only tell me now,

14:57.840 --> 14:58.440
Aunt?

14:59.030 --> 15:00.440
I've spent almost half my life

15:00.440 --> 15:02.510
at the Purong Hotel.

15:02.690 --> 15:05.800
Even if I haven't made any contributions,
I've worked hard.

15:05.800 --> 15:06.920
Aunt,

15:07.800 --> 15:08.840
at a time like this,

15:08.840 --> 15:10.370
why are you telling me this?

15:10.850 --> 15:11.980
Why?

15:12.600 --> 15:13.200
You should

15:13.320 --> 15:14.720
ask yourself about this.

15:15.270 --> 15:16.730
The person who let you down

15:17.000 --> 15:18.440
is yourself.

15:29.790 --> 15:30.510
Aunt.

15:32.050 --> 15:33.450
Your criticism is right.

15:35.150 --> 15:36.630
I have disappointed you.

15:37.630 --> 15:38.600
I'll go back

15:39.270 --> 15:40.870
and think it over carefully.

15:41.110 --> 15:41.820
I'm sorry.

15:42.160 --> 15:43.420
Please don't be angry.

15:44.120 --> 15:45.120
I'll leave now.

15:56.090 --> 15:56.720
Ms. Wei,

15:56.750 --> 15:58.280
should we notify the board?

16:00.150 --> 16:01.200
No need.

16:01.670 --> 16:03.190
We are family after all.

16:04.270 --> 16:05.470
A scolding is enough.

16:06.790 --> 16:08.530
I hope he behaves himself

16:08.630 --> 16:10.760
and doesn't cause me any more trouble.

16:19.760 --> 16:20.400
Miyu.

16:20.420 --> 16:20.990
Mr. Ji.

16:25.860 --> 16:26.460
Come.

16:27.960 --> 16:28.440
Sit.

16:35.790 --> 16:36.590
What's wrong?

16:37.610 --> 16:39.080
New Zealand Yuntian Group

16:39.080 --> 16:40.630
is coming to Shanghai
for a bidding meeting project.

16:40.630 --> 16:42.060
I want to give it another try.

16:42.060 --> 16:42.910
How?

16:42.940 --> 16:45.010
I want to go directly
to their New Zealand headquarters

16:45.010 --> 16:47.040
to meet the director of
the International Marketing Department,

16:47.040 --> 16:47.990
Eric Liang,

16:48.750 --> 16:50.000
and try to bring the bidding meeting

16:50.000 --> 16:51.440
directly to Purong.

16:52.440 --> 16:54.640
This case is key to the performance VAM.

16:55.120 --> 16:57.040
What reason do you have to convince me?

16:57.040 --> 16:58.470
I'm already familiar with all of

16:58.470 --> 17:00.000
their historical choices.

17:00.270 --> 17:00.870
If I can't get it,

17:00.870 --> 17:03.200
I'm willing to take full responsibility.

17:06.510 --> 17:07.069
Okay.

17:07.829 --> 17:09.069
Let me think about it.

17:09.710 --> 17:11.170
I'll wait to hear from you.

17:23.880 --> 17:25.550
About Miyu's application
to go to New Zealand,

17:25.550 --> 17:27.079
are you going to approve it?

17:27.859 --> 17:29.120
I'm thinking about it.

17:29.830 --> 17:30.640
Do you know how many
percentage points we are away

17:30.640 --> 17:33.110
from the 30% goal?

17:34.550 --> 17:35.310
Four points.

17:35.540 --> 17:37.240
If we can bring over

17:37.240 --> 17:38.530
Yuntian Group's bidding meeting,

17:38.530 --> 17:39.870
we have a chance to win.

17:40.030 --> 17:40.880
I know.

17:41.940 --> 17:43.310
That is exactly why

17:43.750 --> 17:45.420
I am considering if she can do it.

17:45.420 --> 17:46.940
I understand how you feel,

17:47.350 --> 17:48.350
but you must know

17:48.870 --> 17:50.460
Miyu is the best person

17:50.510 --> 17:51.370
to push this project forward.

17:51.370 --> 17:52.510
Because no one in the sales department

17:52.510 --> 17:54.070
knows this case better than she does,

17:54.070 --> 17:56.200
or can better empathize
with your pressure and burden.

17:56.200 --> 17:57.200
She is helping you.

17:57.200 --> 17:58.240
I know all of this.

18:00.590 --> 18:02.590
If she succeeds, everyone is happy.

18:03.240 --> 18:05.240
If not, it becomes a career mistake.

18:05.350 --> 18:07.270
The bidding meeting is imminent.

18:07.370 --> 18:09.070
It might be a huge challenge for her,

18:09.070 --> 18:10.240
but there is no time left

18:10.240 --> 18:11.900
for you to hesitate and think.

18:13.110 --> 18:14.640
I understand your anxiety,

18:14.750 --> 18:15.400
but this challenge

18:15.400 --> 18:17.100
is also an opportunity for her.

18:17.100 --> 18:19.560
So I appreciate her
volunteering this time.

18:19.590 --> 18:21.200
I think as the general manager,

18:21.200 --> 18:22.590
you should trust her.

18:39.110 --> 18:40.110
Mr. Xue,

18:40.220 --> 18:41.420
what brings you here?

18:42.960 --> 18:45.000
Your application to go to New Zealand

18:45.000 --> 18:46.060
has been approved.

18:46.350 --> 18:47.270
You leave tonight.

18:47.270 --> 18:48.470
Get ready.

18:48.570 --> 18:50.030
The Office will book the ticket

18:50.030 --> 18:51.360
and send it to your phone.

18:51.360 --> 18:51.990
Okay.

18:52.020 --> 18:53.300
Thank you, Mr. Xue.

18:53.590 --> 18:54.650
No need to thank me.

18:55.010 --> 18:56.280
Mr. Ji signed it.

18:57.000 --> 18:57.790
He also knows

18:57.790 --> 18:59.510
you're doing this
for the hotel's performance.

18:59.510 --> 19:01.350
He asked me to stop by and tell you

19:01.720 --> 19:03.180
thanks for your hard work.

19:04.820 --> 19:05.610
Not at all.

19:05.890 --> 19:10.100
[Purong Hotel]

19:07.150 --> 19:08.550
Then go pack up.

19:08.690 --> 19:09.490
Okay.

19:11.100 --> 19:11.790
And,

19:13.420 --> 19:16.460
are you two going
to keep going on like this?

19:19.440 --> 19:20.720
I've never seen him

19:20.720 --> 19:22.350
this depressed before.

19:23.000 --> 19:25.110
Of course, I know two professionals

19:25.110 --> 19:26.700
always have this or that conflict.

19:26.700 --> 19:28.870
Aren't adult relationships complex?

19:28.900 --> 19:30.770
But I believe you are mature enough.

19:30.770 --> 19:31.580
Right?

19:35.550 --> 19:37.350
If you find love, don't let it go.

19:41.610 --> 19:42.200
Alright.

19:42.260 --> 19:44.460
[Purong Hotel]

19:42.370 --> 19:43.270
Then I wish you

19:43.960 --> 19:44.720
a safe trip.

20:15.680 --> 20:16.880
Why are you here?

20:19.000 --> 20:19.930
Can we talk?

20:23.670 --> 20:24.470
About what?

20:27.330 --> 20:29.390
Are we going to keep giving each other

20:29.590 --> 20:30.850
the silent treatment?

20:33.240 --> 20:33.890
Right.

20:34.540 --> 20:36.270
Regarding the art exhibition,

20:36.510 --> 20:38.400
I didn't consider your feelings.

20:38.920 --> 20:39.830
It's my fault.

20:40.450 --> 20:41.340
I'm sorry.

20:41.610 --> 20:42.480
Ji Feng.

20:42.780 --> 20:44.810
We are not teenagers

20:44.920 --> 20:46.470
playing dating games.

20:46.920 --> 20:48.310
What I want isn't that when I get mad,

20:48.310 --> 20:50.270
you just say sorry to coax me.

20:51.200 --> 20:51.880
What I care about is

20:51.880 --> 20:53.400
whether we have the most basic

20:53.400 --> 20:54.880
equality and honesty.

20:55.850 --> 20:58.440
Are we not equal

20:59.310 --> 21:00.830
and honest with each other?

21:00.830 --> 21:02.510
When we first met,

21:02.660 --> 21:05.350
you hid the evidence
of my ex-husband's cheating.

21:05.350 --> 21:06.830
I can understand that.

21:06.830 --> 21:08.670
It was out of your professional stance.

21:08.670 --> 21:12.540
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

21:08.720 --> 21:10.000
Later, you chose not to tell me

21:10.000 --> 21:11.750
about your past with Ms. Jiang.

21:11.750 --> 21:12.830
I can accept that

21:12.830 --> 21:14.200
because it's your privacy.

21:14.200 --> 21:15.350
But now,

21:15.350 --> 21:17.110
we are already together.

21:17.140 --> 21:18.590
We are in the same boat,

21:18.590 --> 21:20.620
facing common goals and difficulties.

21:20.620 --> 21:23.020
Yet, you still choose to
keep me in the dark.

21:23.240 --> 21:24.440
You know what? Sometimes,

21:24.440 --> 21:26.400
lies can be a form of protection.

21:26.430 --> 21:27.730
That's the problem.

21:27.880 --> 21:28.920
You know better than anyone else

21:28.920 --> 21:30.350
what I've been through.

21:30.430 --> 21:31.180
Miyu.

21:32.090 --> 21:32.720
I...

21:32.920 --> 21:35.860
We both need some space
to think about us.

21:36.980 --> 21:38.510
Let's take some time apart.

21:46.180 --> 21:47.590
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

22:05.750 --> 22:07.510
Sir, to Pudong International Airport.

22:07.510 --> 22:08.400
Okay.

22:11.080 --> 22:13.070
The industry is buzzing

22:13.070 --> 22:14.510
that Dianjiangchun made

22:14.510 --> 22:16.270
an impressive comeback.

22:16.480 --> 22:17.350
So, you were able to

22:17.350 --> 22:18.960
get out of the slump

22:18.960 --> 22:20.440
in such a short time.

22:20.440 --> 22:21.770
How did you do it?

22:21.960 --> 22:22.920
First of all,

22:23.030 --> 22:25.680
I want to thank my fans
for their support and care.

22:25.680 --> 22:26.880
Please rest assured.

22:27.110 --> 22:29.200
I have a great team,

22:29.220 --> 22:30.070
friends,

22:30.090 --> 22:32.030
and people who care about me around me.

22:32.030 --> 22:33.650
Dianjiangchun will not disappear.

22:33.650 --> 22:36.000
I won't let down
anyone who believes in me.

22:36.400 --> 22:37.110
Thank you.

22:54.430 --> 22:56.660
[Miyu]

23:58.750 --> 23:59.920
Let's get a divorce.

24:02.400 --> 24:03.860
What are you trying to say?

24:04.270 --> 24:05.310
Nothing.

24:06.430 --> 24:08.030
It's not your first divorce.

24:14.720 --> 24:15.200
Recently,

24:15.200 --> 24:17.160
getting along with your family,

24:17.990 --> 24:18.830
I know your parents

24:18.830 --> 24:20.690
have a lot of complaints about me.

24:21.260 --> 24:23.060
To be honest, I'm exhausted too.

24:23.720 --> 24:24.580
In fact, people

24:25.160 --> 24:26.810
should believe in destiny.

24:28.260 --> 24:30.270
When destiny between people is over,

24:30.270 --> 24:31.440
it's just over.

24:31.930 --> 24:33.000
Don't force it.

24:33.300 --> 24:34.490
The way you are now,

24:35.880 --> 24:37.480
there is no way you can give me

24:37.670 --> 24:38.600
and the baby

24:38.880 --> 24:40.470
a better future.

24:41.010 --> 24:42.340
I don't want your money.

24:42.800 --> 24:43.840
I get the baby.

24:45.750 --> 24:47.280
Take good care of yourself.

24:48.850 --> 24:50.160
For us,

24:51.430 --> 24:52.800
this is the best relief.

25:00.440 --> 25:01.240
Sign it.

25:04.530 --> 25:06.180
Can you cook some porridge for me?

25:06.180 --> 25:07.550
My stomach is not feeling well.

25:07.550 --> 25:09.110
Can you just order some takeout yourself?

25:09.110 --> 25:11.770
Won't the takeout be cold
by the time it arrives?

25:13.310 --> 25:14.140
Nie Yucheng,

25:16.060 --> 25:17.740
I'm not your servant.

25:17.860 --> 25:19.060
If you think I

25:19.090 --> 25:20.190
don't serve you well enough,

25:20.190 --> 25:21.680
I'll get you a housemaid, okay?

25:21.680 --> 25:23.030
Why do you keep squatting there?

25:23.030 --> 25:23.880
Did you hear me?

25:23.880 --> 25:24.510
I heard you.

25:24.510 --> 25:25.610
I heard you.

25:26.070 --> 25:26.960
My stomach hurts.

25:26.960 --> 25:28.160
Could you pour me a glass of hot water?

25:28.160 --> 25:29.160
Your stomach never hurt

25:29.160 --> 25:30.590
until I started talking about
serious matters.

25:30.590 --> 25:31.790
Just endure the pain.

25:33.480 --> 25:34.050
Mom.

25:36.290 --> 25:37.350
Where is Zhenzhen?

25:39.510 --> 25:40.580
She didn't come.

25:41.310 --> 25:42.920
Just you alone?

25:43.790 --> 25:45.790
I'm the one bringing
in the income.

25:45.810 --> 25:47.160
I'm out early and back late

25:47.160 --> 25:48.400
every day, pregnant.

25:48.400 --> 25:49.310
Do you think I want this life?

25:49.310 --> 25:50.720
With Nie Yucheng like this now,

25:50.720 --> 25:51.510
if I stop working

25:51.510 --> 25:52.550
and earning,

25:52.550 --> 25:53.920
how will this family survive?

25:53.920 --> 25:54.680
All our family savings

25:54.680 --> 25:56.960
have been spent on his medical treatment.

25:56.960 --> 25:58.680
Did you ever ask me?

25:58.680 --> 25:59.880
Did I ever agree to all these?

25:59.880 --> 26:01.190
Did you ever discuss this with me?

26:01.190 --> 26:01.680
Well...

26:02.150 --> 26:03.760
Discuss what?

26:03.910 --> 26:05.440
When a family member gets sick,

26:05.440 --> 26:06.440
shouldn't saving their life come first?

26:06.440 --> 26:07.270
What about me?

26:09.020 --> 26:11.340
Do I have to sacrifice my whole future

26:11.550 --> 26:13.350
to live an exhausted half-life?

26:37.160 --> 26:37.960
Beibei.

26:38.590 --> 26:39.400
Beibei.

26:39.530 --> 26:40.660
Grandma is here.

26:40.960 --> 26:42.110
Grandma is here.

26:43.440 --> 26:44.450
Beibei.

26:45.280 --> 26:45.960
Give me the baby.

26:45.960 --> 26:46.510
Who are you?

26:46.510 --> 26:46.830
Give him to me.

26:46.830 --> 26:48.310
Stop acting crazy, okay?

26:48.330 --> 26:49.680
I'm his mother.

26:49.800 --> 26:50.550
Even if we divorce,

26:50.550 --> 26:51.940
the baby will definitely be with me.

26:51.940 --> 26:53.420
It's not your turn to snatch him.

26:53.420 --> 26:54.350
What divorce?

26:55.570 --> 26:57.100
What are you up to now?

26:57.350 --> 26:59.370
Divorcing now would be too easy on you.

26:59.370 --> 27:00.130
Let me tell you,

27:00.130 --> 27:00.940
don't even think about it.

27:00.940 --> 27:03.340
Stop making things hard on yourself, okay?

27:05.400 --> 27:07.000
Your son has already signed.

27:10.220 --> 27:12.220
[Husband: Nie Yucheng]
[Wife: Lu Zhenzhen]

27:14.160 --> 27:14.990
Lu Zhenzhen,

27:15.010 --> 27:16.230
you heartless thing.

27:16.230 --> 27:17.350
You shameless vixen!

27:17.350 --> 27:19.070
You've ruined all the good fortune

27:19.070 --> 27:20.960
Yucheng was meant to have.

27:20.960 --> 27:21.880
Alright.

27:21.880 --> 27:23.550
You keep saying
the same things over and over.

27:23.550 --> 27:24.880
I'm tired of hearing it.

27:25.070 --> 27:25.550
Get out.

27:25.870 --> 27:26.870
Get out now.

27:26.890 --> 27:28.900
You're not allowed
to take anything from here.

27:28.900 --> 27:31.160
Do you even understand the marriage law?

27:31.170 --> 27:31.640
This house

27:31.640 --> 27:33.270
is marital property
between Nie Yucheng and me.

27:33.270 --> 27:34.590
It should be split in half upon divorce.

27:34.590 --> 27:35.640
Either you make it quick,

27:35.640 --> 27:36.400
give me 5 million,

27:36.400 --> 27:37.360
and I'll leave immediately.

27:37.360 --> 27:38.720
If you don't have the ability
to give me this money,

27:38.720 --> 27:40.070
then shut your mouth.

27:40.090 --> 27:41.200
I'll buy his share of the house.

27:41.200 --> 27:42.080
You buy it then.

27:42.180 --> 27:44.360
If you have the ability,
bring 5 million to buy it!

27:44.360 --> 27:45.190
Don't worry.

27:45.210 --> 27:46.690
My lawyer will contact you.

27:46.690 --> 27:48.110
Hurry up and pack your things
to leave now.

27:48.110 --> 27:48.830
If you don't leave,

27:48.830 --> 27:50.630
I'll call the building manager.

27:50.810 --> 27:52.280
Leave my grandson to me.

27:52.510 --> 27:54.310
I will take him with me if I leave.

27:55.070 --> 27:55.960
Can you stop being crazy?

27:55.960 --> 27:58.160
What does this child have to do with you?

27:59.000 --> 28:00.070
Let me tell you,

28:00.350 --> 28:01.950
this child's surname is Nie.

28:02.350 --> 28:03.950
He will only suffer with you.

28:04.110 --> 28:05.630
Our family should raise him.

28:05.630 --> 28:06.640
Look closely.

28:06.920 --> 28:08.000
Look closely.

28:08.760 --> 28:10.340
Who in your family
does this child look like?

28:10.340 --> 28:12.540
What does he have to do with your family?

28:49.080 --> 28:51.150
[Outpatient Building]

28:51.220 --> 28:54.290
[Result Interpretation:
Probability of paternity is 0.9999%]

28:54.290 --> 28:55.130
[Test Result]

28:55.160 --> 28:56.410
[Paternity DNA Test Report]

28:56.430 --> 28:57.930
[for Nie Yucheng and Nie Quan]

29:04.400 --> 29:06.270
[Jiangpu Hospital
Affiliated to Hushi University]

29:06.300 --> 29:08.340
[Semen Analysis Report]

29:06.510 --> 29:07.310
Doctor.

29:07.480 --> 29:08.410
This...

29:08.440 --> 29:09.920
What does this zero mean?

29:11.270 --> 29:12.270
I know

29:12.510 --> 29:13.720
this is

29:13.720 --> 29:15.110
a huge blow to you.

29:16.050 --> 29:17.680
But the values on the report

29:17.710 --> 29:19.080
are just instantaneous results.

29:17.750 --> 29:18.770
[Jiangpu Hospital
Affiliated to Hushi University]

29:18.800 --> 29:19.990
[Semen Analysis Report]

29:19.360 --> 29:20.070
So,

29:20.090 --> 29:21.680
don't be too discouraged.

29:42.240 --> 29:43.030
Baby,

29:43.030 --> 29:44.630
you're going to see your dad.

29:44.640 --> 29:45.920
Are you happy?

29:47.150 --> 29:48.420
Please come in, Sir.

29:56.810 --> 29:58.360
Come here, Mr. Wei.

30:08.820 --> 30:09.980
You can leave.

30:31.160 --> 30:33.620
Why are you looking for me
at a time like this?

30:33.640 --> 30:35.840
Your direct boss just got into trouble.

30:36.030 --> 30:38.120
I barely managed to keep you out of it.

30:38.140 --> 30:38.830
Didn't I tell you

30:38.830 --> 30:40.430
to keep a low profile lately?

30:40.490 --> 30:41.750
What are you afraid of?

30:43.850 --> 30:44.980
Have some tea first.

30:51.870 --> 30:54.330
There's no denying
who this baby belongs to.

30:55.400 --> 30:56.400
Look, Mr. Wei.

30:57.050 --> 30:59.180
The baby's only just past 100 days old,

30:59.330 --> 31:01.460
and already looks so much like his dad.

31:02.270 --> 31:03.830
This high forehead,

31:03.850 --> 31:05.320
chubby nose,

31:05.510 --> 31:07.350
and these big, dark,

31:07.370 --> 31:08.700
bright eyes.

31:13.070 --> 31:13.930
Zhenzhen.

31:14.200 --> 31:15.160
I just remembered

31:15.160 --> 31:16.050
I have an urgent matter to attend to.

31:16.050 --> 31:17.750
I really have to go now.

31:18.350 --> 31:19.510
If anything comes up later,

31:19.510 --> 31:20.510
just contact Secretary Wu directly.

31:20.510 --> 31:21.510
It's the same.

31:21.720 --> 31:22.440
Okay.

31:22.920 --> 31:25.780
Then I'll come by your house
for a visit another day.

31:31.880 --> 31:33.150
What are you visiting for?

31:33.150 --> 31:34.610
Who are you going to visit?

31:34.720 --> 31:35.510
You just carry a baby

31:35.510 --> 31:37.000
to extort me, right?

31:39.180 --> 31:40.700
Don't wake the baby.

31:45.030 --> 31:45.590
Mr. Wei.

31:46.110 --> 31:47.550
I thought I was being too subtle

31:47.550 --> 31:49.080
and you didn't understand.

31:49.960 --> 31:51.510
The report makes it very clear

31:51.510 --> 31:53.240
whether the child is yours.

31:56.880 --> 31:57.780
[DNA Paternity Test Report]

31:57.810 --> 31:58.800
[for Nie Quan and Wei Siyuan]

31:58.820 --> 32:00.060
[Paternal probability: 99.999%]

32:02.290 --> 32:04.530
[Conclusion]

32:08.640 --> 32:09.640
Didn't I tell you

32:09.640 --> 32:11.000
to get an abortion?

32:12.330 --> 32:13.330
I'm his mother.

32:13.360 --> 32:15.180
Whether to keep it or not is my choice.

32:15.180 --> 32:17.490
Then what do you want from me now?

32:17.520 --> 32:18.410
Calm down.

32:18.440 --> 32:19.920
I'm not forcing you to acknowledge him.

32:19.920 --> 32:21.450
I just want you to do me a favor

32:21.450 --> 32:23.110
so I can raise him alone

32:23.110 --> 32:24.590
and give him a better life.

32:24.990 --> 32:26.320
What if I don't help you?

32:26.920 --> 32:28.270
Then I can't guarantee

32:28.290 --> 32:29.950
that your wife won't find out.

32:38.810 --> 32:39.910
Alright, tell me.

32:40.020 --> 32:41.140
How can I help you?

32:41.700 --> 32:43.230
Make me the Sales Director.

32:44.810 --> 32:46.360
You have quite an appetite.

32:46.390 --> 32:47.680
You're already a Sales Manager.

32:47.680 --> 32:49.760
Isn't the money you make
enough to raise a child?

32:49.760 --> 32:50.460
Mr. Wei,

32:50.640 --> 32:52.540
do I need to remind you

32:52.720 --> 32:54.290
that if you don't promote me,

32:54.290 --> 32:56.180
Ji Feng will promote Xu Miyu?

32:56.430 --> 32:59.190
Your right-hand men have already
been taken out by him.

32:59.190 --> 33:00.250
If this continues,

33:00.530 --> 33:02.790
how much of a chance
do you think you have?

33:04.820 --> 33:05.860
Here's the case.

33:06.420 --> 33:07.910
Ji Feng just went to my aunt

33:07.930 --> 33:09.770
and filed a serious complaint against me.

33:09.770 --> 33:10.700
The one in my family,

33:10.700 --> 33:11.660
that tigress,

33:11.990 --> 33:13.180
is not to be trifled with.

33:13.180 --> 33:14.800
I can't afford to offend her either.

33:14.800 --> 33:15.800
At this juncture,

33:15.830 --> 33:17.190
if I rashly promote you,

33:17.240 --> 33:18.350
aren't you afraid my...

33:18.350 --> 33:20.550
That depends on your own tricks.

33:20.900 --> 33:23.560
You've been running
the hotel for so many years.

33:23.590 --> 33:25.050
To promote one of your own,

33:25.400 --> 33:27.800
do you still need someone else's approval?

33:27.850 --> 33:28.840
Besides,

33:28.990 --> 33:32.110
I know exactly how you
and Director Qian have been

33:32.430 --> 33:34.160
lining your pockets together.

33:34.330 --> 33:35.330
Promote me,

33:35.360 --> 33:36.480
and with my cooperation,

33:36.480 --> 33:38.210
you'll only get more benefits.

33:38.270 --> 33:39.130
What do you say?

33:44.850 --> 33:45.850
Please help

33:45.870 --> 33:47.550
your own flesh and blood.

34:13.030 --> 34:13.860
Great.

34:14.400 --> 34:16.659
Xu Miyu is getting more and more amazing.

34:16.770 --> 34:18.670
She made our hotel stand out
among so many competitors,

34:18.670 --> 34:20.239
even beating Kuanli.

34:23.179 --> 34:24.570
Are you listening to me?

34:29.969 --> 34:30.969
I heard you.

34:31.710 --> 34:33.400
You said Miyu is amazing.

34:35.570 --> 34:38.810
We got the bidding meeting
from Yuntian Group.

34:38.929 --> 34:40.659
Why do you look unhappy?

34:41.840 --> 34:42.590
I'm not.

34:43.420 --> 34:44.940
I'm your senior.

34:44.960 --> 34:47.560
Do you think I can't tell
if you're happy or not?

34:51.030 --> 34:51.989
I am very happy.

34:54.060 --> 34:55.590
You don't look happy at all.

35:13.950 --> 35:14.590
Morning.

35:18.300 --> 35:20.780
♪ Just lift your head, oh ♪

35:21.980 --> 35:23.880
♪ Don't look back ♪

35:25.090 --> 35:26.910
♪ I've already learned ♪

35:27.490 --> 35:31.290
♪ If it's not mine, I won't force it ♪

35:28.510 --> 35:30.230
Ms. Xu.

35:30.230 --> 35:31.710
You are so amazing.

35:31.710 --> 35:32.230
You have no idea

35:32.230 --> 35:33.440
when I received
the email from Yuntian Group,

35:32.310 --> 35:33.800
♪ No matter how you force it ♪

35:33.440 --> 35:35.010
how excited I am!

35:34.510 --> 35:38.950
♪ It'll only turn into a long,
endless wait ♪

35:35.550 --> 35:36.720
That wasn't just an email.

35:36.720 --> 35:38.510
That's our team's annual bonus.

35:38.510 --> 35:39.360
Exactly.

35:39.360 --> 35:40.440
I'm so happy.

35:39.690 --> 35:42.550
♪ Waiting to make peace with myself ♪

35:41.810 --> 35:43.920
After this bidding meeting is completed,

35:43.300 --> 35:45.750
♪ And waiting to meet someone again ♪

35:43.920 --> 35:45.110
let's have a good celebration.

35:45.110 --> 35:45.880
Okay?

35:46.030 --> 35:46.840
Okay, Ms. Xu.

35:46.240 --> 35:47.970
♪ Wave goodbye ♪

35:46.840 --> 35:47.520
Okay.

35:50.030 --> 35:50.880
Ms. Xu.

35:52.070 --> 35:54.330
Mr. Ji asked you
to go to the meeting room.

35:54.520 --> 35:55.250
Okay.

36:38.630 --> 36:39.270
Everyone.

36:39.440 --> 36:41.020
We have just 1 month left

36:41.070 --> 36:42.980
before the VAM agreement settlement date.

36:42.980 --> 36:43.670
Ms. Xu

36:43.670 --> 36:46.470
won us the Yuntian Group
bidding meeting project.

36:46.550 --> 36:47.710
This is both our hope

36:47.710 --> 36:49.230
and a test for us.

36:49.630 --> 36:51.230
We must go all out.

36:52.150 --> 36:53.230
Director Lu, Director Bai.

36:53.230 --> 36:54.000
-Yes.
-Yes.

36:54.000 --> 36:55.190
I'll give you three days.

36:55.190 --> 36:56.440
The marketing department
and the Front Office

36:56.440 --> 36:58.260
must both provide
their respective reception plans.

36:58.260 --> 36:58.960
Yes.

37:04.670 --> 37:05.670
I will announce a personnel appointment

37:05.670 --> 37:07.150
for the sales department.

37:10.800 --> 37:14.040
This is Meng Jie, the new director
of the sales department.

37:14.040 --> 37:15.630
She will be fully responsible for

37:15.630 --> 37:18.230
the sales department's
future work meetings.

37:18.550 --> 37:19.550
Hello, everyone.

37:19.550 --> 37:21.630
I hope we can work well together.

37:21.630 --> 37:22.360
Thank you.

37:23.190 --> 37:24.510
Wasn't it supposed to be Ms. Xu?

37:24.510 --> 37:25.280
What happened?

37:25.280 --> 37:26.540
This is so unexpected.

37:30.590 --> 37:31.700
Any objections?

37:38.280 --> 37:39.140
Director Meng.

37:39.480 --> 37:40.510
For this bidding meeting,

37:40.510 --> 37:42.070
all sales department employees need to

37:42.070 --> 37:43.550
form groups and participate

37:43.550 --> 37:45.330
in customer development for each project.

37:45.330 --> 37:46.110
We will

37:46.440 --> 37:47.480
use this opportunity to develop

37:47.480 --> 37:48.640
our potential customers.

37:48.640 --> 37:49.400
Okay.

37:49.400 --> 37:52.110
But I need someone to assist me.

37:53.280 --> 37:54.030
Ms. Xu.

37:55.400 --> 37:56.920
You are most familiar with
the content of the bidding meeting.

37:56.920 --> 37:57.730
For the time being,

37:57.730 --> 37:59.230
please cooperate more with Director Meng.

37:59.230 --> 38:00.120
The specific details

38:00.120 --> 38:01.850
can be synchronized after the meeting.

38:01.850 --> 38:02.440
Okay.

38:06.520 --> 38:07.370
Mr. Ji.

38:11.190 --> 38:12.590
Why did you have a meeting

38:12.820 --> 38:14.160
without calling me?

38:15.120 --> 38:16.280
It's just some trivial matters.

38:16.280 --> 38:17.630
I didn't dare to bother you, Mr. Wei.

38:17.630 --> 38:18.630
What do you mean by bother?

38:18.630 --> 38:19.630
That's a bit much.

38:21.190 --> 38:22.280
I just heard that you recently

38:22.280 --> 38:25.140
appointed a new director
for the sales department.

38:25.730 --> 38:27.880
I figured they are my future colleagues,

38:27.880 --> 38:30.210
so I came over
specifically to take a look.

38:32.050 --> 38:33.180
By the way, Mr. Ji,

38:33.330 --> 38:35.540
I also have
a new personnel appointment here.

38:35.540 --> 38:37.340
I'd like to ask for your opinion.

38:38.180 --> 38:39.580
Please go ahead, Mr. Wei.

38:39.800 --> 38:41.980
There's a manager in the sales department
named Lu Zhenzhen.

38:41.980 --> 38:43.110
You know her, right?

38:46.860 --> 38:47.510
Of course.

38:47.510 --> 38:48.360
I completely trust

38:48.360 --> 38:49.960
the newly appointed Director Meng

38:49.960 --> 38:51.500
can lead the sales department well.

38:51.500 --> 38:52.760
But after all, she just arrived.

38:52.760 --> 38:54.480
She isn't familiar with many things yet,

38:54.480 --> 38:55.630
and needs someone by her side

38:55.630 --> 38:57.440
to help out and coordinate.

38:57.460 --> 38:58.510
I heard that

38:58.510 --> 38:59.540
Ms. Lu

38:59.560 --> 39:00.680
is very capable

39:00.710 --> 39:02.440
and was Purong's top sales rep.

39:02.630 --> 39:03.550
Although

39:03.570 --> 39:05.250
she hasn't been here long either,

39:05.250 --> 39:07.620
the sales department
is in need of people right now.

39:07.620 --> 39:09.630
We should recruit talents
without overstressing qualifications.

39:09.630 --> 39:10.400
So,

39:10.950 --> 39:12.130
I want to promote her to

39:12.130 --> 39:13.730
vice director of the sales department.

39:13.730 --> 39:14.580
Mr. Ji,

39:15.030 --> 39:16.030
what do you think?

39:24.670 --> 39:25.360
Susan.

39:25.780 --> 39:27.690
Remember to handle this
for Mr. Wei after the meeting.

39:27.690 --> 39:28.770
Okay, Mr. Ji.

39:31.100 --> 39:31.790
Alright.

39:32.190 --> 39:32.830
That's it.

39:33.710 --> 39:34.690
You guys continue.

39:34.690 --> 39:35.400
Okay.
